column1: Table 18. Supplemental data for state governments (final)
Series title:  Justice Expenditure and Employment Extracts 2009, NCJ 247018
Data source:  Justice Expenditure and Employment Extracts Program (JEE)
Table 18. Supplemental data for state governments (revised)
Note:  "Estimated population" represents resident U.S. population (50 states excluding the District of Columbia) from the Bureau of the Census, Current Population Reports, July 2010.
a/ "Personal income" is from the U.S. Department of Commerce, Survey of Current Business, August 2009.
b/ "Total general expenditure" excludes utilities, State-operated liquor stores, and insurance trust benefits.
c/ "General functions only" FTE excludes utilities, and State-operated liquor stores.
